{"id":2470,"date":"2021-04-11T15:36:42","date_gmt":"2021-04-11T15:36:42","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/?p=2470"},"modified":"2021-09-19T16:30:16","modified_gmt":"2021-09-19T16:30:16","slug":"cach-lam-yen-sao-hanh-nhan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/cach-lam-yen-sao-hanh-nhan\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/tac-dung-yen-chung-duong-phen\/\">y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n<\/a>, g\u00e0 h\u1ea7m t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn,&#8230; th\u00ec <strong><em>y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh<\/em><\/strong> nh\u00e2n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb th\u01a1m ngon v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lifenest s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1ea9m b\u1ed5 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1edbn c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f3n \u0103n n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u1eebng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o&nbsp;<\/b><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2474\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2474\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2474 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan.jpg\" alt=\"Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2474\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5t dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao&nbsp;<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/\">Y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o<\/a> hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i&#8221;cao l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ef9 v\u1ecb&#8221; c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: V\u1edbi 18 lo\u1ea1i axit amin c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean t\u1ed1 vi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: C\u00e1c vi ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 Mn, Cu, Zn, Br trong t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong vi\u1ec7c \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh v\u00e0 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi nh\u1edb cho b\u1ed9 n\u00e3o. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng an th\u1ea7n, gi\u00fap ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u gi\u1ea5c h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>B\u1ed5 m\u00e1u<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Trong y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o gi\u00e0u protein v\u00e0 Fe \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ea3n sinh m\u00e1u trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p hemoglobin &#8211; ch\u1ea5t v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n oxy cho c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Ch\u1ea5t threonine c\u00f3 trong y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o gi\u00fap h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh collagen l\u00e0 elastin. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da. Khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Glycine s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, ch\u1ed1ng oxy hoa da, gi\u1ea3m m\u1edd c\u00e1c v\u1ebft t\u00e0n nhang, n\u00e1m da. Gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Gi\u00fap h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Trong y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a nguy\u00ean t\u1ed1 Cr, d\u00f9 v\u1edbi h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 \u00edt nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng k\u00edch th\u00edch h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0103n ngon mi\u1ec7ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>H\u1ec7 x\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n ch\u1eafc kh\u1ecfe<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng canxi, Phenylalanine c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p vitamin D t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea5p thu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn canxi \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea7n x\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng sinh l\u00fd<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: V\u1edbi h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng acid amin v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 \u1edf c\u1ea3 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb suy nh\u01b0\u1ee3c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi \u1ed1m d\u1eady, ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt hay m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh ung th\u01b0,&#8230; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1edd c\u00e1c axit amin nh\u01b0 Proline, Glucosamine,&#8230;&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<blockquote><p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/tac-dung-yen-sao\/\">B\u1eadt m\u00ed 9 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ( t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn ) kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3><b>H\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n&nbsp;<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &#8220;n\u1eef ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t&#8221; v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 \u00edch cho s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a h\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn:&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2473\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2473\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2473 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-2.jpg\" alt=\"H\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1eef ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t\u201d\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-2.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-2-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-2-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2473\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cn\u1eef ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t\u201d&nbsp;<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>T\u1ed1t cho h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111au tim<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Trong h\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o \u0111\u01a1n &#8211; b\u00e3o h\u00f2a, protein v\u00e0 potassium gi\u00fap h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Vitamin E trong h\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh v\u1ec1 tim.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>\u1ed4n \u0111\u1ecbnh huy\u1ebft \u00e1p<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Trong h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a h\u00e0m l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn Acid folic v\u00e0 Magnesium gi\u00fap h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p Homocystein &#8211; \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ea3ng trong m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng potassium trong <a href=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/huyet-ap-thap-an-yen\/\">y\u1ebfn gi\u00fap \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a huy\u1ebft \u00e1p<\/a> lu\u00f4n \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p thu dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: H\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec1m h\u00f3a h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m s\u1ef1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 axit v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t. Gi\u00fap h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ec7nh t\u1eadt.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: Tinh d\u1ea7u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 trong h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nhanh no gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0103n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. C\u00e1c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e9o ph\u00ec n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ed5 sung h\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n v\u00e0o kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ea7n \u0103n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ea5t x\u01a1 c\u00f3 trong h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u00f2n gi\u00fap ch\u1ed1ng t\u00e1o b\u00f3n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0102n h\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f2n gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng b\u1ec7nh ung th\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ung th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u00e0ng, ung th\u01b0 tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ung th\u01b0 v\u00fa. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f2n gi\u00fap ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba s\u1ecfi m\u1eadt, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh Alzheimer v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u00f3n t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 m\u00f3n \u0103n th\u01a1m ngon, b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o gi\u00fap b\u1ed3i b\u1ed5 c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho h\u1ec7 tim m\u1ea1ch. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00f3n \u0103n ngon gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft n\u0103ng n\u00f3ng. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng Lifenest kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u00f3n \u0103n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh nh\u00e9.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2472\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2472\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2472 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-3.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-3.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-3-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/04\/yen-sao-hanh-nhan-3-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2472\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n&nbsp;<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb:&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn: 5\u201310g<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ea1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n: 80g<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1 th\u00eca h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eafng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t \u00edt l\u00e1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u1eaft m\u1ecfng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3 th\u00eca b\u1ed9t ng\u00f4&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">300ml n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n:&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: \u0110em ng\u00e2m t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn v\u00e0o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1eeb 20-30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 y\u1ebfn n\u1edf \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u01a1i r\u1ed3i \u0111em r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: H\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111em ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc trong v\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn khi m\u1ec1m th\u00ec v\u1edbt ra \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e1o. Ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh xay nhuy\u1ec5n h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t \u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc, l\u1ecdc b\u00e3 v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c xay m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1ea5y n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u00e3. Cho h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n v\u00e0o n\u1ed3i, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 n\u1ea5u ch\u00edn.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Cho y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o v\u00e0o b\u00e1t v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y trong kho\u1ea3ng 15-20 ph\u00fat. Sau khi y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u00edn m\u1ec1m b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 ngu\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: H\u00f2a b\u1ed9t ng\u00f4 c\u00f9ng 1\/2 c\u1ed1c n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i th\u00eam v\u00e0o n\u1ed3i h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n, tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111un s\u00f4i<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Cho h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n ra b\u00e1t, sau \u0111\u00f3 cho y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0ng v\u00e0o. Sau \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u00edt l\u00e1t h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u1eaft m\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed. M\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c khi c\u00f2n n\u00f3ng hay l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n m\u00f3n \u0103n sau khi ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng, c\u00e1ch ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n th\u00ec c\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1556\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1556\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-1556 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/bao-quan-yen-chung.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n m\u00f3n \u0103n sau khi ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/bao-quan-yen-chung.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/bao-quan-yen-chung-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/bao-quan-yen-chung-768x401.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1556\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n m\u00f3n \u0103n sau khi ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn&nbsp;<\/span><\/i><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi ch\u01b0ng, c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eady k\u00edn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n \u1edf trong t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb 2-5 \u0111\u1ed9 C (trong ng\u0103n m\u00e1t c\u1ee7a t\u1ee7 l\u1ea1nh).&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau khi ch\u01b0ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng h\u1ebft th\u00ec b\u1ea1n chia nh\u1ecf th\u00e0nh t\u1eebng ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 trong ng\u0103n m\u00e1t. Vi\u1ec7c chia nh\u1ecf n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00f3n \u0103n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n sau.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u00fa \u00fd y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0ng c\u00f9ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n hay c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 ng\u00e0y. B\u1edfi \u0111a ph\u1ea7n c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n th\u1ea5p d\u1ec5 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n l\u00e2u h\u01a1n b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ri\u00eang t\u1eebng c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u, khi c\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1edbi cho v\u00e0o chung m\u1ed9t ch\u00e9n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e2m n\u00f3ng y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed3i h\u1ea5p c\u00e1ch th\u1ee7y trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00f3n \u0103n th\u01a1m v\u00e0 ngon h\u01a1n.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y,Lifenest Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m m\u00f3n y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0. Hy v\u1ecdng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tay ch\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u00f3n \u0103n th\u01a1m ngon b\u1ed5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng!&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 y\u1ebfn s\u00e0o ch\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e8n, g\u00e0 h\u1ea7m t\u1ed5 y\u1ebfn,&#8230; th\u00ec y\u1ebfn ch\u01b0ng h\u1ea1nh nh\u00e2n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb th\u01a1m ngon v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Lifenest s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2472,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_seopress_robots_primary_cat":"none"},"categories":[19],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2470"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2470"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/yensaokhanhhoa.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2470\/r